入面<br />\n空管主任返唔到工，航班升降效率低左就會開始delay/cancel架喇</span>"},{"pid":"d31666f3d1b9eb788be7337eb5986876c63894af","tid":1493563,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:01:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aeb05d9a9dc634affe75b7e5f0315ab8b9a855b2","tid":1493563,"uid":188758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:07:07.000Z","msg":"做啦 香港人 <br />\n忍痛三日可以結束呢場仗<br />\n我知好多人重係有包袱<br />\n但我地已經冇得退<br />\n要明嘅已經明晒<br />\n已經唔使care 唔明嘅人點諗<br />\n<br />\n簡單一句<br />\n有手足受傷 被捕 毒打 酷刑 暴動罪慘d<br />\n定係和理非 遊客受阻重要d?<br />\n<br />\n如果機場不合作運動可以唔使香港人再受傷<br />\n可以聲援被炒機場員工<br />\n<br />\n你願意嗎？"},{"pid":"75c9452fe221d83313011d0af714e6ce8b9b8809","tid":1493563,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:11:20.000Z","msg":"824"},{"pid":"efb179bc4fec63017d5b6f6aec4962fbbe66d1ad","tid":1493563,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:13:29.000Z","msg":"行動Post! 推推推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708c5c2ad9a8bf0b986e54f1e471be51ceec6832","tid":1493563,"uid":95092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:23:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0413a430b29c66420a190402212db32b89aae52e","tid":1493563,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:42:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8324d60d83bd6e259e6f1b4c9e0c9574f3c1707","tid":1493563,"uid":150500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f6c09451afc07af4f4898e12ca80093e393a0fb","tid":1493563,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"824"},{"pid":"240c2a4f53fc9f55cf5faa603560ae5a13c18b10","tid":1493563,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislik